							<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2">Benchmark</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								20 LLM Research tasks curated from top-tier conferences and latest papers.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl p-6">
							<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-100 mb-2">ResearchGym</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Sandbox your custom agents with Dockerized tools & evaluation loops.
							</p>
						</div>
